title: Clemson Hottie Owns Up To Bet And Gets Tigers Paw Ass Tattoo After Team’s National Title Win

organizations.name: tigers paw ass tattoo after team

text:
Back in November, we wrote about Peyton , a Donald Trump supporter and Clemson student who promised to get a “lock her up” Hiillary Clinton ass tat after Trump pulled off the upset win in the presidential election. Despite starting a successful GoFundMe campaign for the “Lock her up” tat she never went through with it for whatever reason. 
It seems like Peyton likes making ass tat bets because back in August she said she would get one if the Clemson Tigers won the National Championship.
Making this deal again this year – if Clemson can win the natty I'll get a tiger paw ass tat
— Peyton Darnell (@peyton_darnelll) August 28, 2016 

This time Peyton did own up to her promise and got this Tiger Paw tattoo on her ass following the Tigers win over Alabama on Monday. 
More pics to come later but pic.twitter.com/rNhgfkoYre 
— Peyton Darnell (@peyton_darnelll) January 12, 2017 
On 8/27/16 I tweeted that if clemson can win the natty, I'll get a tiger paw ass tat. A bet is a bet ¯\_(ツ)_/¯ #NattyChamps #tiger4life #sorrytomywholefamily 
A photo posted by Peyton Darnell (@peytondarnell) on Jan 12, 2017 at 1:42pm PST 
One ass tat down, one more to go.
